 ('3', '3', 'en_us', 'We just installed Craft!', '<p>Craft is the CMS that’s powering Kentstatestudentmedia.com. It’s beautiful, powerful, flexible, and easy-to-use, and it’s made by Pixel &amp; Tonic. We can’t wait to dive in and see what it’s capable of!</p>\n<!--pagebreak-->\n<p>This is even more captivating content, which you couldn’t see on the News index page because it was entered after a Page Break, and the News index template only likes to show the content on the first page.</p>\n<p>Craft: a nice alternative to Word, if you’re making a website.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'centerCenter', '{\"id\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"archived\":0,\"locale\":\"en_us\",\"localeEnabled\":1,\"slug\":null,\"uri\":null,\"dateCreated\":null,\"dateUpdated\":null,\"root\":null,\"lft\":null,\"rgt\":null,\"level\":null,\"searchScore\":null,\"elementId\":0,\"metaType\":\"template\",\"metaPath\":\"\",\"seoMainEntityCategory\":\"CreativeWork\",\"seoMainEntityOfPage\":\"WebPage\",\"seoTitle\":\"We just installed Craft!\",\"seoDescription\":\"\",\"seoKeywords\":\"\",\"seoImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageTransform\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"\",\"openGraphType\":\"\",\"robots\":\"\",\"seoImageId\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageId\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageId\":\"\",\"seoTitleUnparsed\":\"We just installed Craft!\",\"seoDescriptionUnparsed\":\"\",\"seoKeywordsUnparsed\":\"\",\"seoTitleSource\":\"field\",\"seoTitleSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoDescriptionSource\":\"custom\",\"seoDescriptionSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoKeywordsSource\":\"custom\",\"seoKeywordsSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoImageIdSourceField\":\"heroImage\",\"seoTwitterImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoTwitterImageIdSourceField\":\"heroImage\",\"seoFacebookImageIdSource\":