 ('10', '10', 'en_us', 'A Magazine', '<p>A Magazine is Kent State\'s publication for all things fashion, beauty and culture on campus and beyond. A Magazine focuses on women\'s and men\'s fashion providing its audience with the latest fashion industry news and more in print, online and through social media. It is distributed at Kent State and the Fashion School’s New York studio. A Magazine steps outside just the Kent State campus. From New York City to Florence, Italy and Hong Kong, back to Kent, Ohio, we have students studying and producing content from all over the world<br /></p>', NULL, 'amagksu@gmail.com', '[]', 'Payton', 'Moore', 'Student Leader', NULL, '330-672-2586', 'A Magazine is a visually stunning student-run magazine at Kent State. It is the publication for all things fashion, beauty, accessories and culture on campus and beyond. A focuses on both women\'s and men\'s fashion and has companion website that is updated regularly with extended content and videos, providing students with the latest fashion news. It is distributed at Kent State and the Fashion School’s New York studio.', NULL, NULL, 'Fashion. Beauty. Culture. ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'A Magazine is Kent State’s student-run fashion magazine and is the hub for all things fashion, beauty and culture related', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://www.theamag.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'centerCenter', '{\"id\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"archived\":0,\"locale\":\"en_us\",\"localeEnabled\":1,\"slug\":null,\"uri\":null,\"dateCreated\":null,\"dateUpdated\":null,\"root\":null,\"lft\":null,\"rgt\":null,\"level\":null,\"searchScore\":null,\"elementId\":0,\"metaType\":\"template\",\"metaPath\":\"\",\"seoMainEntityCategory\":\"CreativeWork\",\"seoMainEntityOfPage\":\"WebPage\",\"seoTitle\":\"A Magazine\",\"seoDescription\":\"\",\"seoKeywords\":\"\",\"seoImageTransform\":\"hero\",\"seoFacebookImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageTransform\":\"\",\"