 ('15', '15', 'en_us', 'The Kent Stater', '<p>The Kent Stater is an award-winning student-run newspaper. Reaching more than 9,500 people per issue, the Stater keeps the community up-to-date with campus, local and national news, sports and features. The Stater publishes on Monday and Thursday and has a circulation of 6,000 per day. During the summer months, The Kent Stater runs special print issues and a special start of the school year issue. The Kent Stater publishes online with media partner, TV2 KSU, at KentWired.com.</p>', NULL, 'kentwired@gmail.com', '[]', 'Jimmy', 'Miller', 'Student Leader', NULL, '330-672-2586', 'The Kent Stater is the award-winning, student-run newspaper at Kent State University. Reaching more than 15,000 people per issue, the Stater keeps the community up-to-date with campus, local and national news, sports and features. The Stater publishes on Monday, Wednesday and Thursday and has a circulation of 6,750 per day. During the summer months, The Kent Stater runs special print issues and also runs the annual Orientation issue to welcome new and returning students.', NULL, NULL, 'The Independent Student Newspaper of Kent State University', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The independent news team covering KSU and the Kent community ', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.kentwired.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'centerCenter', '{\"id\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"archived\":0,\"locale\":\"en_us\",\"localeEnabled\":1,\"slug\":null,\"uri\":null,\"dateCreated\":null,\"dateUpdated\":null,\"root\":null,\"lft\":null,\"rgt\":null,\"level\":null,\"searchScore\":null,\"elementId\":0,\"metaType\":\"template\",\"metaPath\":\"\",\"seoMainEntityCategory\":\"CreativeWork\",\"seoMainEntityOfPage\":\"WebPage\",\"seoTitle\":\"The Kent Stater\",\"seoDescription\":\"\",\"seoKeywords\":\"\",\"seoImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageTransform\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"\",\"openGraphType\":\"\",\"robots\":\"\",\"seoImageId\":null,\"seoTwitterImageId\":null,\"seoFacebookImageId\":null,\"seoTitleUnparsed\":\"\",\"seoDescriptionUnparsed\":\"\",\"seoKeywordsUnparsed\":\"\",\"seoTitleSource\":\"field\",\"seoTitleSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoDescriptionSource\":\"custom\",\"seoDescriptionSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoKeywordsSource\":\"custom\",\"seoKeywordsSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoImageIdSourceField\":\"adBundlePhoto\",\"seoTwitterImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoTwitterImageIdSourceField\":\"adBundlePhoto\",\"seoFacebookImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoFacebookImageIdSourceField\":\"adBundlePhoto\",\"seoCommerceVariants\":null,\"__model__\":\"Craft\\\\Seomatic_MetaFieldModel\"}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '2017-02-27 15:21:14', '2017-07-23 19:53:44', '7e622988-7d52-4011-872c-1c063f8dcc6e'),
 ('19', '19', 'en_us', 'Black Squirrel Radio', '<p>Black Squirrel Radio is a student-run radio station committed to providing innovative media content inspired by the community of Kent, Ohio, dedicated to professionalism, integrity, creativity and diversity. With 56 different student-hosted shows airing from 10 a.m. to 2 a.m. everyday, we are committed to providing professional industry experience while continuing to be a platform for experimental programming. Through alternative media content, we aim to grow our audience by becoming the destination for students and alumni to remember what was and experience what is college life in Kent, Ohio.</p>', NULL, 'general email address goes here', '[]', 'Layne', 'Gerbig', 'Student Leader', NULL, '330-xxx-xxxx', 'Black Squirrel Radio (BSR) is a student-run radio station that has 10,000 loyal monthly listeners. BSR features a large selection of urban, rock and local music with numerous local bands and entertainers coming for in-studio performances and interviews. BSR is available at www.blacksquirrelradio.com, iTunes radio under College Stations, the TuneIn app and channels 2-4 and 2-6 though on-campus television.', NULL, NULL, 'Kent State\'s Student-Run Radio Station', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'BSR is Kent State’s student-run radio station providing unique and innovative media content online.', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://www.blacksquirrelradio.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'centerCenter', '{\"id\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"archived\":0,\"locale\":\"en_us\",\"localeEnabled\":1,\"slug\":null,\"uri\":null,\"dateCreated\":null,\"dateUpdated\":null,\"root\":null,\"lft\":null,\"rgt\":null,\"level\":null,\"searchScore\":null,\"elementId\":0,\"metaType\":\"template\",\"metaPath\":\"\",\"seoMainEntityCategory\":\"CreativeWork\",\"seoMainEntityOfPage\":\"WebPage\",\"seoTitle\":\"Black Squirrel Radio\",\"seoDescription\":\"\",\"seoKeywords\":\"\",\"seoImageTransform\":\"\",\