 ('23', '23', 'en_us', 'KentWired', '<p>KentWired.com is the shared website for two Student Media partners, The Kent Stater and TV2 KSU. The site features top news, entertainment, community and campus news, sports and video. KentWired is the place to turn to for everything Kent and Portage County. The site also features classifieds, TV2 newscasts and entertainment shows and a live stream to TV2. KentWired is a key source for news during the summer. With 40,000 unique visitors per month, KentWired is a top news source in Kent and Portage County. </p>', NULL, 'kentwired@gmail.com', '[]', '', '', '', NULL, '330-672-2586', 'KentWired.com is a news organization hosting content created by the collaborative effort of students working in student media at Kent State University. KentWired is the independent news website for the Kent Stater and TV2 and is the year round news source for everything Kent. KentWired has top news, entertainment, sports, and community and campus news. It also features classifieds and live streams for TV2 and Black Squirrel Radio. ', NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The online outlet for The Kent Stater and TV2 KSU and the best breaking news source in Kent and Portage County', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.kentwired.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'centerCenter', '{\"id\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"archived\":0,\"locale\":\"en_us\",\"localeEnabled\":1,\"slug\":null,\"uri\":null,\"dateCreated\":null,\"dateUpdated\":null,\"root\":null,\"lft\":null,\"rgt\":null,\"level\":null,\"searchScore\":null,\"elementId\":0,\"metaType\":\"template\",\"metaPath\":\"\",\"seoMainEntityCategory\":\"CreativeWork\",\"seoMainEntityOfPage\":\"WebPage\",\"seoTitle\":\"KentWired\",\"seoDescription\":\"\",\"seoKeywords\":\"\",\"seoImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageTransform\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"\",\"openGraphType\":\"\",\"robots\":\"\",\"seoImageId\":null,\"se