 ('56', '58', 'en_us', 'About us', '<p><strong>For more than 90 years,</strong> students at Kent State University have been finding ways to tell stories and disseminate vital and compelling information.\n  </p>\n<p>Even before formal journalism education classes had been established, students were chasing leads and documenting the events shaping our history, sharing their work in the Normal High School News and The Chestnut Burr in 1914, The Kentonian in 1915 and eventually the first issue of The Kent Stater on July 29, 1926.</p>\n<p><strong>We now are more than 700 students</strong> working with 10 distinct and independent Student Media partners who create unique content distributed across 34 different outlets on multiple platforms. Our students are supported in their efforts by a strong fabric of faculty advisers, professional staff, university support and, of course, financial support from the students of Kent State University. </p>\n<p>And while the methods have varied since those early publications, our core philosophy has remained constant: empower students to create valued sources and encourage excellence.\n  </p>\n<p><strong>Won’t you join us and continue the story?</strong></p>', NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Student Media Today.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '<p>We like to think big. And sometimes our budget can\'t keep up. Your generous gift helps our students build on their big ideas. Your gift can be directed at a specific media partner or go directly to support Student Media in general.  <br /></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Advertise with us!</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Members of the fall 2016 Burr staff pose for a picture. The Burr was recognized as the best student magazine in the country by the Society of Professional Journalists.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'centerCenter', '{\"id\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"archived\":0,\"locale\":\"en_us\",\"localeEnabled\":1,\"slug\":null,\"uri\":null,\"dateCreated\":null,\"dateUpdated\":null,\"root\":null,\"lft\":null,\"rgt\":null,\"level\":null,\"searchScore\":null,\"elementId\":0,\"metaType\":\"template\",\"metaPath\":\"\",\"seoMainEntityCategory\":\"CreativeWork\",\"seoMainEntityOfPage\":\"WebPage\",\"seoTitle\":\"About us\",\"seoDescription\":\"\",\"seoKeywords\":\"\",\"seoImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageTransform\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"\",\"openGraphType\":\"\",\"robots\":\"\",\"seoImageId\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageId\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageId\":\"\",\"seoTitleUnparsed\":\"About us\",\"seoDescriptionUnparsed\":\"\",\"seoKeywordsUnparsed\":\"\",\"seoTitleSource\":\"field\",\"seoTitleSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoDescriptionSource\":\"custom\",\"seoDescriptionSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoKeywordsSource\":\"custom\",\"seoKeywordsSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoImageIdSourceField\":\"heroImage\",\"seoTwitterImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoTwitterImageIdSourceField\":\"heroImage\",\"seoFacebookImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoFacebookImageIdSourceField\":\"heroImage\",\"seoCommerceVariants\":null,\"__model__\":\"Craft\\\\Seomatic_MetaFieldModel\"}', 'Our mission-driven leadership begins here', '<p><strong>STUDENT MEDIA EMPOWERS STUDENTS</strong> through practical, collaborative and professional learning opportunities within an independent, student-led and multi-platform media framework.</p>\n<p><strong>OUR STUDENTS CREATE </strong>valued sources of journalism, information, entertainment and advertising and develop meaningful connections with our core audiences.\n</p>\n<p><strong>WE ENCOURAGE EXCELLENCE</strong>, leadership and accountability as students become innovative, ethical and skilled media producers within a diverse and global society.</p>', '<p>Paragraph description of awards can go here.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '2017-03-16 18:11:56', '2017-07-25 00:39:30', '13261c0b-f807-4755-b432-6dabac5a1e5c'),
 ('57', '59', 'en_us', 'Media Partners', '<p>Ten distinct media partners make up the engine that drives Kent State Student Media forward. Each partner is a unique and independent student organization. They have opted to join together for mutual benefit under the banner of Student Media. At the top of each group is the selected editor, general manager or president who each \"have sole authority to determine content for the media they lead and in turn take full responsibility for the content decisions made.\" They work with their faculty advisers, and others, to provide professional, high quality content for their audiences. Learn about each media partner below. </p>', NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The engine of Student Media', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'centerCenter', '{\"id\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"archived\":0,\"locale\":\"en_us\",\"localeEnabled\":1,\"slug\":null,\"uri\":null,\"dateCreated\":null,\"dateUpdated\":null,\"root\":null,\"lft\":null,\"rgt\":null,\"level\":null,\"searchScore\":null,\"elementId\":0,\"metaType\":\"template\",\"metaPath\":\"\",\"seoMainEntityCategory\":\"CreativeWork\",\"seoMainEntityOfPage\":\"WebPage\",\"seoTitle\":\"Media Partners\",\"seoDescription\":\"\",\"seoKeywords\":\"\",\"seoImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageTransform\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"\",\"openGraphType\":\"\",\"robots\":\"\",\"seoImageId\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageId\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageId\":\"\",\"seoTitleUnparsed\":\"Media Partners\",\"seoDescriptionUnparsed\":\"\",\"seoKeywordsUnparsed\":\"\",\"seoTitleSource\":\"field\",\"seoTitleSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoDescriptionSource\":\"custom\",\"seoDescriptionSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoKeywordsSource\":\"custom\",\"seoKeywordsSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoImageIdSourceField\":\"heroImage\",\"seoTwitterImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoTwitterImageIdSourceField\":\"heroImage\",\"seoFacebookImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoFacebookImageIdSourceField\":\"heroImage\",\"seoCommerceVariants\":null,\"__model__\":\"Craft\\\\Seomatic_MetaFieldModel\"}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '2017-03-16 18:12:46', '2017-07-23 00:50:39', '57fa80e5-3b72-4d48-9fbe-73f241d20602'),
 ('58', '60', 'en_us', 'Get Involved', '<p>Student Media is open to any students, staff or faculty at Kent State. Start as early as your freshman year and get involved in any of dozens of positions across our 10 Student Media partners. Gain important experience that will set you apart from your fellow students. Come share your voice and gain practical experience to help launch your career. To get started, check out current openings below or contact Kevin Dilley, director of Student Media, at kdilley@kent.edu.</p>', NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Student Media is open to any students, staff or faculty. Get started as early as your freshman year in any of dozens of positions across our 10 media partners.  Student Media gives you the experience you need to set you apart. Utilize the chance to share your voice and gain practical experience to help launch your career.', NULL, NULL, 'Start your freshman year. Stay until you graduate. ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'centerCenter', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '2017-03-16 18:13:51', '2017-07-17 20:44:47', '89e67a7d-4178-48fa-895b-7dd52c79ccb5'),
 ('59', '61', 'en_us', 'Advertise with Student Media', '<p>We are your direct access to more than 70,000 people. We connect you to our audience through award-winning digital, print, film and broadcast media.</p>\n<p>We have been serving Kent State University and the Kent community for more than 80 years with independent student-produced media. We have the outlets you need to reach the target audience you want.</p>\n<p>We look forward to partnering with you and look forward to your success.</p>', NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'It starts with you. ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Whatever your business needs, Kent State Student Media has the creative service to attain your goal. We offer video and audio production, design services, photography, DJ services, writing and marketing services. We manage projects and budgets of all sizes. Kent State Student Media provides high quality work at a competitive price. Contact our office today to find out how we can help you excel in your field.  \n  </p>', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'centerCenter', '{\"id\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"archived\":0,\"locale\":\"en_us\",\"localeEnabled\":1,\"slug\":null,\"uri\":null,\"dateCreated\":null,\"dateUpdated\":null,\"root\":null,\"lft\":null,\"rgt\":null,\"level\":null,\"searchScore\":null,\"elementId\":0,\"metaType\":\"template\",\"metaPath\":\"\",\"seoMainEntityCategory\":\"CreativeWork\",\"seoMainEntityOfPage\":\"WebPage\",\"seoTitle\":\"Advertise with Student Media\",\"seoDescription\":\"For more than 90 years, students at Kent State University have been finding ways to tell stories and disseminate vital and compelling information.\",\"seoKeywords\":\"\",\"seoImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageTransform\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"\",\"openGraphType\":\"\",\"robots\":\"\",\"seoImageId\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageId\":\"\",\"seoFaceboo