 ('60', '62', 'en_us', 'Contact Student Media', '<p>We\'d love to hear from you, whether it\'s about getting involved with Student Media, reaching out about individual partners and their content, or for advertising opportunities. </p>\n<ul><li>For advertising contact us at <a href=\"mailto:ads@ksustudentmedia.com\">ads@ksustudentmedia.com</a>, 330-672-6306, or drop by our office during business hours, Monday through Friday 8 a.m to 5 p.m. in 205 Franklin Hall on the Kent State University Kent campus. </li><li>For general Student Media questions, reach out to Director of Student Media, Kevin Dilley, at <a href=\"mailto:kdilley@kent.edu\">kdilley@kent.edu</a>  or 330-672-0887. You\'ll also find him in 205 Franklin Hall. </li></ul>', NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '330-672-6306', 'Feel free to contact us! Shoot us an e-mail at ads@ksustudentmedia.com, call us at 330-672-6306 or drop by our office during business hours.', NULL, NULL, 'How can we help?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '205 Franklin Hall, Hilltop Drive Kent, Ohio 44240', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'centerCenter', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '2017-03-16 18:15:45', '2017-07-17 20:45:16', '26429fb1-6847-4a0e-8b08-c8f65cd97187'),
