 ('114', '165', 'en_us', 'Lorie Bednar', '<p>Lorie Bednar joined Kent State’s School of Journalism and Mass Communication in 2015 as an administrative clerk in the Kent State Student Media office. She now shares her time between both offices. </p>\n<p><strong>Words to Live By:</strong></p>\n<p>Be Where Your Feet Are – Anonymous</p>\n<p><strong>Personal</strong>:</p>\n<p>I am a graduate of Kent State University and love everything about my Alma mater. If you don’t find me on campus, chances are you may run into me downtown and throughout Kent, which is the place I call home with my husband and three kids. Two of my greatest achievements are winning an Associated Press award for enterprise writing and being the illustrator of a book jacket.</p>\n<p><strong>I can help you with:</strong></p>\n<ul><li><p>KEYS!</p></li><li><p>Staff lists</p></li><li><p>Job offers</p></li><li><p>Travel</p></li><li>General questions</li></ul>', NULL, 'lbednar@kent.edu', '[\"officeStaff\"]', 'Lorie', 'Bednar', 'Office Manager/Miracle Worker', NULL, '330-672-0883', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'centerCenter', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '2017-04-24 17:37:01', '2017-07-23 19:54:18', '5e0b009f-baba-4aef-b7db-adf004400e1c'),
 ('115', '166', 'en_us', 'Support Us', '<p>We like to think big. And sometimes our budget can\'t keep up. Your generous gift helps our students build on their big ideas. Your gift can be directed at a specific media partner or go directly to support Student Media in general. Past support has helped us send students to cover election night 2016 in New York City, send other students to California to cover the NCAA basketball tournament, and has helped other students produce full-length feature films. No gift is too small. We\'ll put 100% of your donation to work immediately. </p>', NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'We\'ll go farther together', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'centerCenter', '{\"id\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"archived\":0,\"locale\":\"en_us\",\"localeEnabled\":1,\"slug\":null,\"uri\":null,\"dateCreated\":null,\"dateUpdated\":null,\"root\":null,\"lft\":null,\"rgt\":null,\"level\":null,\"searchScore\":null,\"elementId\":0,\"metaType\":\"template\",\"metaPath\":\"\",\"seoMainEntityCategory\":\"CreativeWork\",\"seoMainEntityOfPage\":\"WebPage\",\"seoTitle\":\"Support Us\",\"seoDescription\":\"\",\"seoKeywords\":\"\",\"seoImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageTransform\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"\",\"openGraphType\":\"\",\"robots\":\"\",\"seoImageId\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageId\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageId\":\"\",\"seoTitleUnparsed\":\"Support Us\",\"seoDescriptionUnparsed\":\"\",\"seoKeywordsUnparsed\":\"\",\"seoTitleSource\":\"field\",\"seoTitleSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoDescriptionSource\":\"custom\",\"seoDescriptionSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoKeywordsSource\":\"custom\",\"seoKeywordsSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoImageIdSourceField\":\"heroImage\",\"seoTwitterImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoTwitterImageIdSourceField\":\"heroImage\",\"seoFaceboo