 ('568', '45', '8', '235', 'en_us', '7', '', '{\"typeId\":\"8\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Kevin Dilley\",\"slug\":\"kevin-dilley\",\"postDate\":1489335420,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"20\":[\"23\"],\"1\":\"<p>Kevin serves Student Media by providing management of our business and advising operations. He also works with student leaders, the board, faculty and other key partners to set a strategic direction for Student Media and mentors and advises student leaders. &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Words to Live By:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>If you want to go fast, go alone. If you want to go far, go together. &nbsp;~ origin unknown.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Personal:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>I\\u2019ve traveled to Siberia, Malaysia, Mexico and 46 of 50 states in the U.S. I love going places and meeting new people, but I always yearn to return home. For me, that\\u2019s in Hudson with my two children, mi media naranja (si, hablo espa\\u00f1ol), and Pancho, my very best friend because, well he\\u2019s a dog and I\\u2019m a man. I hold degrees in journalism and visual communication from the University of Missouri and Ohio University. I\\u2019ve worked as a reporter, writer, photojournalist, editor, designer, web designer, project manager, consultant, professor and adviser. I love what I do because I\\u2019m constantly inspired by my students who bring ideas, enthusiasm, opportunity and optimism to this place every day.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>I can help you with:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul><li><p>General questions<\\/p><\\/li><li><p>Strategic planning<\\/p><\\/li><li><p>Idea development<\\/p><\\/li><li><p>Budgets<\\/p><\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"4\":\"kdilley@kent.edu\",\"5\":[\"director\",\"nonVoting\",\"officeStaff\"],\"6\":\"Kevin \",\"19\":[\"292\"],\"8\":\"Director of Student Media\",\"7\":\"Dilley\",\"10\":\"330-672-4603\"}}', '2017-06-13 19:19:02', '2017-06-13 19:19:02', '064d600d-df57-4c19-a958-6c5cfd22d628'),
 ('569', '62', '13', '235', 'en_us', '20', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Contact Student Media\",\"slug\":\"contact\",\"postDate\":1489688145,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>We\'d love to hear from you, whether it\'s about getting involved with Student Media, reaching out about individual partners and their content, or for advertising opportunities.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul><li>For advertising contact us at <a href=\\\"mailto:ads@ksustudentmedia.com\\\">ads@ksustudentmedia.com<\\/a>, 330-672-6306, or drop by our office during business hours, Monday through Friday 8 a.m to 5 p.m. in 205 Franklin Hall on the Kent State University Kent campus.&nbsp;<\\/li><li>For general Student Media questions, reach out to Director of Student Media, Kevin Dilley, at <a href=\\\"mailto:kdilley@kent.edu\\\">kdilley@kent.edu<\\/a>  or 330-672-0887. You\'ll also find him in 205 Franklin Hall.&nbsp;<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"13\":[\"271\"],\"21\":\"How can we help?\"}}', '2017-06-13 19:31:04', '2017-06-13 19:31:04', '236b2882-8cf8-432f-b161-1f244d617ad4'),
 ('570', '101', '4', '235', 'en_us', '13', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Student Media Advertising\",\"slug\":\"student-media-ad-sales\",\"postDate\":1492116120,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"31\":\"\",\"1\":\"<p>Our Student Media Advertising and Marketing team can help your campus department or local business reach the audience you are seeking. Our staff of account executives will work hand-in-hand to ensure your message is delivered effectively, efficiently and within your budget. Kent State Student Media has 10 different media partners and more than 30 outlets to reach your target market. We provide advertising, promotional item design and ordering, design services, video and audio production, and mobile DJ services. Contact our team today to get started.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"4\":\"ads@ksustudentmedia.com\",\"36\":\"1\",\"13\":[\"220\"],\"14\":\"\",\"68\":\"\",\"10\":\"330-672-6303\",\"29\":\"An innovative, energetic team connecting our clients to our media partners and signature brands such as KentWired, KentCribs and Transitions\",\"26\":\"\",\"21\":\"A multi-service, multim-platform solution\"}}', '2017-06-13 19:32:17', '2017-06-13 19:32:17', '109a86bc-1d2f-4830-bfd3-3a46417719dc'),
 ('571', '14', '4', '235', 'en_us', '16', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"The Burr\",\"slug\":\"the-burr\",\"postDate\":1488208860,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"31\":[\"68\"],\"1\":\"<p>The Burr Magazine is Kent State University\\u2019s first student magazine, made by the students for the students. The Burr publishes a semesterly&nbsp;magazine that explores big issues and burning ideas, as well as fascinating people and the consuming preoccupations of its college audience. Each issue contains a compelling mix of how-to articles, original reporting and personal essays. TheBurr.com features Web and multimedia stories, as well as blogs on lifestyle issues, including relationships, fashion and entertainment.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\",\"4\":\"theburrmagazine@gmail.com\",\"36\":\"1\",\"13\":[\"242\"],\"14\":[\"48\"],\"68\":\"\",\"10\":\"330-672-2947\",\"29\":\"Exploring big issues, burning ideas, fascinating people and preoccupations of its audience\",\"26\":{\"145\":{\"type\":\"socialMediaBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"socialName\":\"instagram\",\"address\":\"https:\\/\\/www.instagram.com\\/theburrmagazine\\/\"}},\"146\":{\"type\":\"socialMediaBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"socialName\":\"twitter\",\"address\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/TheBurrMagazine\"}},\"147\":{\"type\":\"socialMediaBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"socialName\":\"facebook\",\"address\":\"https:\\/\\/facebook.com\\/theburrmagazine\\/\"}},\"148\":{\"type\":\"socialMediaBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"socialName\":\"website\",\"address\":\"http:\\/\\/theburr.com\\/\"}}},\"21\":\"Providing award-winning student journalism since 1986\"}}', '2017-06-14 17:38:33', '2017-06-14 17:38:33', 'b1d93694-3dd6-41c0-95f4-549f0dbb9c92'),
