 ('579', '2', '1', '235', 'en_us', '53', '', '{\"typeId\":\"1\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Kent State Student Media\",\"slug\":\"homepage\",\"postDate\":1495818871,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"61\":[\"58\"],\"55\":\"<p>We are your direct access to more than 70,000 people. We connect you to our audience through award-winning digital, print, film and broadcast media.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We have been serving Kent State University and the Kent community for more than 80 years with independent student-produced media. We have the outlets you need to reach the target audience you want.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We look forward to partnering with you and look forward to your success.<\\/p>\",\"62\":[\"61\"],\"63\":\"Advertise With Us\",\"1\":\"<p>Kent State Student Media makes the connections you need. Whether you are a student looking for media experience, a community member wanting to share your story, or an audience member after quality news, information and entertainment, we deliver for you across 34 outlets through print, digital and social media platforms. &nbsp;<br><\\/p>\",\"12\":\"Student Media Connects\",\"13\":[\"240\",\"242\",\"243\",\"241\",\"244\",\"238\"],\"17\":\"\",\"64\":\"Our Media Partners\",\"21\":\"Ten media partners. Seven hundred students. One mission. \",\"22\":\"https:\\/\\/player.vimeo.com\\/video\\/210945217\",\"65\":\"Take a 90-second tour of Kent State Student Media \"}}', '2017-06-14 18:05:53', '2017-06-14 18:05:53', '4e95e8e6-61cd-4b11-b55b-ac339331b316'),
