 ('651', '329', '4', '235', 'en_us', '4', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Kent Cribs\",\"slug\":\"kent-cribs\",\"postDate\":1498766820,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"31\":[\"69\"],\"1\":\"<p>The premiere apartment finder for Kent, Ohio and Kent State University. &nbsp;If you\'re looking for a place to live, you\'ll find ads with full-color photos, floor plans, videos and direct contact to property owners. If you\'re looking to reach students, staff, faculty and community members, this is your place. We get visitors from all over Ohio and the world looking for the perfect place to call home for four years or more.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"4\":\"\",\"36\":\"\",\"13\":\"\",\"14\":[\"331\"],\"68\":[\"330\"],\"10\":\"\",\"29\":\"\",\"26\":\"\",\"72\":\"\",\"21\":\"Your apartment search just got easier\",\"89\":\"\"}}', '2017-06-29 20:18:10', '2017-06-29 20:18:10', '8295b86f-0323-4653-a81e-6f765d00a724'),
