 ('654', '45', '8', '235', 'en_us', '8', '', '{\"typeId\":\"8\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Kevin Dilley\",\"slug\":\"kevin-dilley\",\"postDate\":1489335420,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"20\":\"\",\"1\":\"<p>Kevin serves Student Media by providing management of our business and advising operations. He also works with student leaders, the board, faculty and other key partners to set a strategic direction for Student Media and mentors and advises student leaders. &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Words to Live By:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>If you want to go fast, go alone. If you want to go far, go together. &nbsp;~ origin unknown.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Personal:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>I\\u2019ve traveled to Siberia, Malaysia, Mexico and 46 of 50 states in the U.S. I love going places and meeting new people, but I always yearn to return home. For me, that\\u2019s in Hudson with my two children, mi media naranja (si, hablo espa\\u00f1ol), and Pancho, my very best friend because, well he\\u2019s a dog and I\\u2019m a man. I hold degrees in journalism and visual communication from the University of Missouri and Ohio University. I\\u2019ve worked as a reporter, writer, photojournalist, editor, designer, web designer, project manager, consultant, professor and adviser. I love what I do because I\\u2019m constantly inspired by my students who bring ideas, enthusiasm, opportunity and optimism to this place every day.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>I can help you with:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul><li><p>General questions<\\/p><\\/li><li><p>Strategic planning<\\/p><\\/li><li><p>Idea development<\\/p><\\/li><li><p>Budgets<\\/p><\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"4\":\"kdilley@kent.edu\",\"5\":[\"director\",\"nonVoting\",\"officeStaff\"],\"6\":\"Kevin \",\"19\":[\"292\"],\"8\":\"Director of Student Media\",\"7\":\"Dilley\",\"10\":\"330-672-0887\"}}', '2017-06-29 20:47:36', '2017-06-29 20:47:36', '9b1e5408-74ad-4607-91cb-9d090eccf3fa'),
 ('655', '166', '22', '235', 'en_us', '11', '', '{\"typeId\":\"22\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Support Us\",\"slug\":\"support-us\",\"postDate\":1493318469,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>We like to think big. And sometimes our budget can\'t keep up. Your generous gift helps our students build on their big ideas. Your gift can be directed at a specific media partner or go directly to support Student Media in general. &nbsp;Past support has helped us send students to cover election night 2016 in New York City, send other students to California to cover the NCAA basketball tournament, and has helped other students produce full-length feature films. No gift is too small. We\'ll put 100% of your donation to work immediately.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"13\":[\"248\"],\"21\":\"We\'ll go farther together\"}}', '2017-06-29 20:50:18', '2017-06-29 20:50:18', 'bf5bdf79-f81f-4a67-9fd3-172a2974b5c5'),
