 ('710', '14', '4', '235', 'en_us', '18', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"The Burr\",\"slug\":\"the-burr\",\"postDate\":1488208860,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"31\":[\"68\"],\"1\":\"<p>The Burr Magazine is Kent State University\\u2019s first student magazine, made by the students for the students. The Burr publishes a semesterly&nbsp;magazine that explores big issues and burning ideas, as well as fascinating people and the consuming preoccupations of its college audience. Each issue contains a compelling mix of how-to articles, original reporting and personal essays. TheBurr.com features Web and multimedia stories, as well as blogs on lifestyle issues, including relationships, fashion and entertainment.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"4\":\"theburrmagazine@gmail.com\",\"36\":\"1\",\"13\":[\"242\"],\"14\":[\"48\"],\"68\":[\"314\"],\"10\":\"330-672-2947\",\"29\":\"Exploring big issues, burning ideas, fascinating people and preoccupations of its audience\",\"26\":{\"145\":{\"type\":\"socialMediaBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"socialName\":\"instagram\",\"address\":\"https:\\/\\/www.instagram.com\\/theburrmagazine\\/\"}},\"146\":{\"type\":\"socialMediaBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"socialName\":\"twitter\",\"address\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/TheBurrMagazine\"}},\"147\":{\"type\":\"socialMediaBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"socialName\":\"facebook\",\"address\":\"https:\\/\\/facebook.com\\/theburrmagazine\\/\"}},\"148\":{\"type\":\"socialMediaBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"socialName\":\"website\",\"address\":\"http:\\/\\/theburr.com\\/\"}}},\"72\":\"\",\"21\":\"Providing award-winning student journalism since 1986\",\"89\":\"https:\\/\\/www.theburr.com\"}}', '2017-06-30 16:10:44', '2017-06-30 16:10:44', 'ef1fb0f8-c817-47a9-90fb-789eb4b9754b'),
 ('711', '15', '4', '235', 'en_us', '28', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"The Kent Stater\",\"slug\":\"kent-stater\",\"postDate\":1488208860,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"31\":[\"68\"],\"1\":\"<p>The Kent Stater is an award-winning student-run newspaper. Reaching more than 9,500 people per issue, the Stater keeps the community up-to-date with campus, local and national news, sports and features. The Stater publishes on Monday and Thursday and has a&nbsp;circulation of 6,000 per day. During the summer months, The Kent Stater runs special print issues and a special start of the school year issue. The Kent Stater publishes online with media partner, TV2 KSU, at KentWired.com.<\\/p>\",\"4\":\"kentwired@gmail.com\",\"36\":\"1\",\"13\":[\"244\"],\"14\":[\"51\"],\"68\":[\"327\"],\"10\":\"330-672-2586\",\"29\":\"The independent news team covering KSU and the Kent community \",\"26\":{\"227\":{\"type\":\"socialMediaBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"socialName\":\"twitter\",\"address\":\" https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/kentwired\"}},\"228\":{\"type\":\"socialMediaBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"socialName\":\"instagram\",\"address\":\"https:\\/\\/www.instagram.com\\/kentwired\\/\"}},\"229\":{\"type\":\"socialMediaBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"socialName\":\"facebook\",\"address\":\"https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/KentWired\\/\"}},\"230\":{\"type\":\"socialMediaBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"socialName\":\"website\",\"address\":\"http:\\/\\/www.kentwired.com\\/\"}}},\"72\":\"\",\"21\":\"The Independent Student Newspaper of Kent State University\",\"89\":\"https:\\/\\/www.kentwired.com\"}}', '2017-06-30 16:13:53', '2017-06-30 16:13:53', '3356503e-23ae-4200-b509-1914f3887686'),
 ('712', '24', '4', '235', 'en_us', '24', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Luna Negra\",\"slug\":\"luna-negra\",\"postDate\":1488484140,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"31\":[\"68\"],\"1\":\"<p>Luna Negra, though sometimes under different names, has been around since 1956. It began under the English department, where it found its footing within the campus\\u2019s cultural atmosphere. Since then, the publication has been a staple of the university, witnessing the path Kent State has taken through the decades. We have published works describing the culture of collegiate 1950s, the Kent State shootings, and 9\\/11; the literary pieces published by Luna Negra, written by the students themselves, have chronicled every major cultural and historical event of America. Since its inception, and still to today, Luna Negra is run by students and filled with student content. We strive to foster creative activity across campus and seek to be the keeper and encourager of the student body\\u2019s creative spirit.<\\/p>\",\"4\":\"lunanegramag@gmail.com\",\"36\":\"1\",\"13\":[\"308\"],\"14\":[\"53\"],\"68\":[\"325\"],\"10\":\"\",\"29\":\"Kent State\\u2019s literary and arts journal publishing a blend of poetry, prose, photography and illustration\",\"26\":{\"129\":{\"type\":\"socialMediaBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"socialName\":\"facebook\",\"address\":\"https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/lunanegramag\\/\"}},\"130\":{\"type\":\"socialMediaBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"socialName\":\"instagram\",\"address\":\"https:\\/\\/www.instagram.com\\/lunanegramagazine\\/\"}},\"131\":{\"type\":\"socialMediaBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"socialName\":\"twitter\",\"address\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/lunanegramag\"}},\"132\":{\"type\":\"socialMediaBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"socialName\":\"website\",\"address\":\"http:\\/\\/www.lunanegramag.com\\/\"}}},\"72\":\"\",\"21\":\"Kent State\'s Literary and Arts 