 ('747', '165', '8', '267', 'en_us', '4', '', '{\"typeId\":\"8\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Lorie Bednar\",\"slug\":\"lorie-bednar\",\"postDate\":1493055420,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"20\":\"\",\"1\":\"<p>Lorie Bednar joined Kent State\\u2019s School of Journalism and Mass Communication in 2015 as an administrative clerk in the Kent State Student Media office. She now shares her time between both offices.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Words to Live By:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Be Where Your Feet Are \\u2013 Anonymous<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Personal<\\/strong>:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>I am a graduate of Kent State University and love everything about my Alma mater. If you don\\u2019t find me on campus, chances are you may run into me downtown and throughout Kent, which is the place I call home with my husband and three kids. Two of my greatest achievements are winning an Associated Press award for enterprise writing and being the illustrator of a book jacket.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>I can help you with:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul><li><p>KEYS!<\\/p><\\/li><li><p>Staff lists<\\/p><\\/li><li><p>Job offers<\\/p><\\/li><li><p>Travel<\\/p><\\/li><li>General questions<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"4\":\"lbednar@kent.edu\",\"5\":[\"officeStaff\"],\"6\":\"Lorie\",\"19\":\"\",\"8\":\"Office Manager\\/Miracle Worker\",\"7\":\"Bednar\",\"10\":\"330-672-3290\"}}', '2017-07-05 17:50:41', '2017-07-05 17:50:41', '903a0916-8427-482e-a6cd-96f62e12307c'),
