 ('867', '59', '10', '1', 'en_us', '15', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Media Partners\",\"slug\":\"media-partners-home\",\"postDate\":1489687966,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>Ten distinct media partners make up the engine that drives Kent State Student Media forward. Each partner is a unique and independent student organization. They have opted to join together for mutual benefit under the banner of Student Media. At the top of each group is the selected editor, general manager or president who each \\\"have sole authority to determine content for the media they lead and in turn take full responsibility for the content decisions made.\\\" They work with their faculty advisers, and others, to provide professional, high quality content for their audiences. Learn about each media partner below.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"13\":[\"249\"],\"100\":{\"seoMainEntityCategory\":\"CreativeWork\",\"seoMainEntityOfPage\":\"WebPage\",\"seoTitleSource\":\"field\",\"seoTitleSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoTitleUnparsed\":\"\",\"seoDescriptionSource\":\"custom\",\"seoDescriptionSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoDescriptionUnparsed\":\"\",\"seoKeywordsSource\":\"custom\",\"seoKeywordsSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoKeywordsUnparsed\":\"\",\"seoImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoImageIdSourceField\":\"heroImage\",\"seoImageId\":\"\",\"seoImageTransform\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoTwitterImageIdSourceField\":\"heroImage\",\"seoTwitterImageId\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageTransform\":\"\",\"openGraphType\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoFacebookImageIdSourceField\":\"heroImage\",\"seoFacebookImageId\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageTransform\":\"\",\"robots\":\"\"},\"72\":\"\",\"21\":\"The engine of Student Media\"}}', '2017-07-23 00:50:39', '2017-07-23 00:50:39', '590de5ae-1f80-47f6-a9b3-708459f42581'),
 ('868', '166', '22', '1', 'en_us', '26', '', '{\"typeId\":\"22\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Support Us\",\"slug\":\"support-us\",\"postDate\":1499350547,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>We like to think big. And sometimes our budget can\'t keep up. Your generous gift helps our students build on their big ideas. Your gift can be directed at a specific media partner or go directly to support Student Media in general. Past support has helped us send students to cover election night 2016 in New York City, send other students to California to cover the NCAA basketball tournament, and has helped other students produce full-length feature films. No gift is too small. We\'ll put 100% of your donation to work immediately.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"77\":{\"334\":{\"type\":\"fundraiserInfo\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"fundraiserTitle\":\"General fundraiser\",\"description\":\"<p>Go here anytime to support your favorite media partner or Student Media in general. <\\/p>\",\"linkName\":\"Support Us\",\"linkUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/secure2.convio.net\\/ksu\\/site\\/SPageNavigator\\/Student_media_designated_giving_form.html#\\/\",\"fundraiserImage\":\"\"}},\"349\":{\"type\":\"fundraiserInfo\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"fundraiserTitle\":\"Test Fundraiser\",\"description\":\"<p>This is just a test to see how this displays as the second fundraiser. <\\/p>\",\"linkName\":\"Test link to support us\",\"linkUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/secure2.convio.net\\/ksu\\/site\\/SPageNavigator\\/Student_media_designated_giving_form.html#\\/\",\"fundraiserImage\":[\"239\"]}}},\"13\":[\"248\"],\"100\":{\"seoMainEntityCategory\":\"CreativeWork\",\"seoMainEntityOfPage\":\"WebPage\",\"seoTitleSource\":\"field\",\"seoTitleSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoTitleUnparsed\":\"\",\"seoDescriptionSource\":\"custom\",\"seoDescriptionSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoDescriptionUnparsed\":\"\",\"seoKeywordsSource\":\"custom\",\"seoKeywordsSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoKeywordsUnparsed\":\"