 ('869', '161', '21', '1', 'en_us', '21', '', '{\"typeId\":\"21\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Student Media Board \",\"slug\":\"board-members\",\"postDate\":1498770287,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p><strong>As a standing University committee<\\/strong>, the Student Media Board serves \\\"as the institutional publisher or de facto licensee and acts in all matters pertaining to those media that are written or broadcast primarily by students and financed primarily by university-sanctioned student fees.\\\" &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>The SMB is primarily responsible for selecting student leaders, approving annual budgets and hearing any grievances that cannot be otherwise resolved. <\\/strong>The SMB does not dictate or determine editorial content for Student Media partners and gives responsibility for day-to-day editorial operations to the selected student leaders. Responsibility for short term business operations and long-term strategy is delegated to the director of Student Media.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>The board is made up of students, staff and faculty across the university, as well as media professionals outside of KSU. These include:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul><li>Faculty members appointed by the faculty senate<\\/li><li>Faculty members appointed by the School of Journalism and Mass Communication faculty advisory committee<\\/li><li>Director of Journalism and Mass Communication<\\/li><li>Director of the Center for Student Involvement<\\/li><li>Students appointed by the Undergraduate Student Government<\\/li><li>A graduate senate student appointee<\\/li><li>JMC undergraduate students<\\/li><li>JMC graduate student&nbsp;<\\/li><li>A media professional<\\/li><li>All selected Student Media leaders, advisers and the director of Student Media serve as non-voting members.&nbsp;<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>Check out the <a href=\\\"#guidelines\\\">guidelines<\\/a>, <a href=\\\"#voting\\\">members<\\/a> and <a href=\\\"#documents\\\">meeting documents<\\/a> below.<br><\\/p>\",\"49\":[\"204\"],\"13\":[\"246\"],\"100\":{\"seoMainEntityCategory\":\"CreativeWork\",\"seoMainEntityOfPage\":\"WebPage\",\"seoTitleSource\":\"field\",\"seoTitleSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoTitleUnparsed\":\"\",\"seoDescriptionSource\":\"custom\",\"seoDescriptionSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoDescriptionUnparsed\":\"\",\"seoKeywordsSource\":\"custom\",\"seoKeywordsSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoKeywordsUnparsed\":\"\",\"seoImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoImageIdSourceField\":\"heroImage\",\"seoImageId\":\"\",\"seoImageTransform\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoTwitterImageIdSourceField\":\"heroImage\",\"seoTwitterImageId\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageTransform\":\"\",\"openGraphType\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoFacebookImageIdSourceField\":\"heroImage\",\"seoFacebookImageId\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageTransform\":\"\",\"robots\":\"\"},\"72\":{\"336\":{\"type\":\"link\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"linkName\":\"University Policy 4-12.1\",\"linkUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.kent.edu\\/policyreg\\/administrative-policy-regarding-student-media-policy-board\"}}},\"21\":\"We\'ll go farther together \"}}', '2017-07-23 00:55:05', '2017-07-23 00:55:05', '6fcae9c8-ffb3-4fd8-aec8-44080df22cde'),
