 ('2', '72', 'en_us', 'Web Ads', '[{\"col3\":\"728 x 90\",\"col1\":\"$195\",\"col5\":\"$215\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"Weekly\"},{\"col3\":\"728 x 90 \",\"col1\":\"$650\",\"col5\":\"$700\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"Monthly\"},{\"col3\":\"960 x 30\",\"col1\":\"$125\",\"col5\":\"$150\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"Weekly\"},{\"col3\":\"960 x 30\",\"col1\":\"$425\",\"col5\":\"$500\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"Monthly\"},{\"col3\":\"300 x 250\",\"col1\":\"$175\",\"col5\":\"$195\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"Weekly\"},{\"col3\":\"300 x 250\",\"col1\":\"$600\",\"col5\":\"$650\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"Monthly\"},{\"col3\":\"180 x 600\",\"col1\":\"$100\",\"col5\":\"$125\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"Weekly\"},{\"col3\":\"180 x 600\",\"col1\":\"$350\",\"col5\":\"$425\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"Monthly\"},{\"col3\":\"120 x 600\",\"col1\":\"$75\",\"col5\":\"$100\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"Weekly\"},{\"col3\":\"120 x 600\",\"col1\":\"$275\",\"col5\":\"$350\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"Monthly\"}]', '<p>Place your ad where the campus and community turns first for breaking news, extended news and entertainment. Each banner ad includes a link to your site, monthly statistics and ad design services.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"col1\":\"Still\",\"col2\":\"Flash\"}]', '2017-03-23 18:10:55', '2017-07-17 19:57:10', '58d90dfb-ed32-43c7-853a-347bbd3bc7a1'),
 ('3', '74', 'en_us', 'Display Ads', '[{\"col3\":\"Full Page\",\"col1\":\"$1,450\",\"col5\":\"$1,100\",\"col2\":\"11\\\" x 21\\\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Front Page\",\"col1\":\"$450\",\"col5\":\"$400 \",\"col2\":\"11\\\" x 3\\\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"2\\/3 Page\",\"col1\":\"$975\",\"col5\":\"$735 \",\"col2\":\"7.23\\\" x 21\\\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"1\\/2 Page\",\"col1\":\"$725\",\"col5\":\"$550 \",\"col2\":\"11\\\" x 10.5\\\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"1\\/4 Page \",\"col1\":\"$375\",\"col5\":\"$275 \",\"col2\":\"5.44\\\" x 10.5\\\" \",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"1\\/8 Page\",\"col1\":\"$175\",\"col5\":\"$130 \",\"col2\":\"5.44\\\" x 5\\\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"1\\/16 Page\",\"col1\":\"$75\",\"col5\":\"$55 \",\"col2\":\"5.44\\\" x 2\\\" \",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '<p>Ads smaller than 1/16 will run on the classifieds page and are priced on an individual basis</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"col1\":\"Local\",\"col2\":\"Campus\\/Non-Profit\"}]', '2017-03-23 18:21:18', '2017-07-17 20:04:59', 'f9c63df7-512f-43c2-aa11-d61d22d9157c'),
 ('4', '75', 'en_us', 'Color Pricing', '[{\"col3\":\"Full Color\",\"col1\":\"$75\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Black + 1 Color\",\"col1\":\"$30\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-03-23 18:27:09', '2017-07-17 20:04:59', 'f4345141-5f57-4e5f-904e-8d916a0e4007'),
 ('7', '82', 'en_us', 'Display Ads', '[{\"col3\":\"Half Page\",\"col1\":\"$195\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Full Page\",\"col1\":\"$275\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Inside Cover\",\"col1\":\"$325\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Back Cover\",\"col1\":\"$400\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '<p><strong>WEB BONUS:</strong></p>\n<p>All magazine ads also\ninclude a banner ad on\nthe magazine’s website\nfor one month.\n</p>\n<p>Additional months can\nbe purchased for only\n<strong>$25 per month.</strong>\n</p>\n<p><strong>MULTI-MAGAZINE\nDISCOUNT</strong>\n</p>\n<p>Run in three or more\nstudent-produced\nmagazines and get\n10% off all ads.\n</p>\n<p>Run in all six magazines\nand get <strong>20% off all ads. </strong></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-04-06 19:25:39', '2017-07-25 18:19:16', 'ddb66fcd-7e4d-4a12-85ec-52f760d558df'),
 ('8', '92', 'en_us', 'Sponsored Tweets', '[{\"col3\":\"Weekly\",\"col1\":\"$85\\/tweet\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Monthly\",\"col1\":\"$75\\/tweet (minimum purchase of 4)\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"(minimum purchase of four)\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Deluxe\",\"col1\":\"$65\\/tweet (minimum purchase of 8)\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"(minimum purchase of eight)\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '<p>Kentwired currently has more than 9,100 followers on its Twitter account. Sponsored tweets can be purchased for any time of day, any day of the week. Limit of one sponsored tweet per day and a maximum of four per week. Tweets may contain up to 131 characters and must include “SPONSORED.” Including hashtags and mentions aid in building traffic and engagement. Tweets may also include creative and/or photos. Monthly statistics will be sent to all advertisers.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-04-13 20:31:54', '2017-07-18 18:39:48', '2a7ad9b3-b2c4-403d-9d05-e5dc628cdd0c'),
 ('9', '97', 'en_us', 'TV 2 Productions', '[{\"col3\":\"Field Shooting\",\"col1\":\"$100\\/hour\\/camera\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"HD Studio Rental\",\"col1\":\"$100\\/hour\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Studio Crew\",\"col1\":\"$25\\/hour\\/person\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Graphic Design\",\"col1\":\"$40\\/hour\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"DVD Menu Designs\",\"col1\":\"$40\\/hour\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Editing\",\"col1\":\"$40\\/hour\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Voiceovers & Acting\",\"col1\":\"$25\\/hour\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Scriptwriting\",\"col1\":\"$25\\/hour\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Web Formatting\",\"col1\":\"$25\\/hour\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '<p>We offer a full spectrum of video production services\nincluding commercials, training videos, seminars,\nconcerts, HD studio rentals, weddings and much more.</p>\n<p>Our production company provides quality, professional\nwork that is cost-effective. Contact Tami Bongiorni at\n330-672-6306 or tbongior@kent.edu for a detailed\nquote on your video project. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-04-13 20:37:01', '2017-07-17 20:13:50', 'd8736285-7bca-42cb-a340-fb93daefe0c5'),
