 ('16', '109', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Print, Web, Twitter, Radio & TV', '$625', '<ul><li>A 1/4-page full color ad in The Kent Stater for one day.</li><li>A 728x90 banner ad on Kentwired.com for one week.</li><li>One sponsored tweet on the @Kentwired handle</li><li>Sixty 10-second live-reads on Black Squirrel Radio within one month.</li></ul>', NULL, '2017-04-14 21:45:58', '2017-07-06 18:42:39', 'cd2b5a2b-d4b1-4498-b326-9060103ec676'),
 ('17', '110', 'en_us', 'Rental Listings', '[{\"col3\":\"Rental Listings\",\"col1\":\"$75\\/month\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '<p>Fill your vacancies faster with a Kentcribs listing. The listing showcases your property with unlimited photos and narrative. Prospective tenants can also email or call you directly from a mobile device. </p>\n<p>Listings include: </p>\n<p>• Name </p><p>• Phone </p><p>• Address </p><p>• Email </p><p>• Web link </p><p>• Photos </p><p>• Price/month/unit </p><p>• Apartment type </p><p>• # rooms &amp; baths </p><p>• Amenities </p><p>• Floor plans </p><p>• Map </p><p>• Unlimited narrative </p><p>• Distance from KSU Student Center</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-04-14 21:49:58', '2017-07-17 19:59:05', 'a1d926f1-a60e-4321-95cf-6d717825197e'),
 ('18', '111', 'en_us', 'Video Pre-Roll', '[{\"col3\":\"Weekly\",\"col1\":\"$125\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Monthly\",\"col1\":\"$450\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '<p>Fifteen-second commercial or video prior to TV2 videos on Kentwired.com. We offer production services if required. Please see page 17 for pricing and more information.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-04-14 21:58:18', '2017-07-17 19:57:10', 'cffe6f16-f09f-4041-b60d-6832dbc8c3e0'),
 ('19', '112', 'en_us', 'Inserts & Post-its', '[{\"col3\":\"Single-Page Insert\",\"col1\":\"$450\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Multi-Page Insert\",\"col1\":\"$500\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"3\\\"x3\\\" or 4\\\"x5\\\" Post-it\",\"col1\":\"$600\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '<p>Post-Its must be printed in a fan-fold and boxed. The unwind direction must be #1 or #3. Insert/Post-it sample must be submitted to Kent State Student Media for approval. Inserts/Post-its must be printed by the client and shipped directly to the printer at least one week prior to insertion. Inserts and Post-Its are within every copy of The Kent Stater. Advertisers should print and ship 6,750 total. Kent State Student Media can arrange the printing of the Post-Its for advertisers for an additional $75. Please ship directly to: Midwest Offset 629 Wabash Avenue NW New Philadelphia, Ohio 44663 800-837-8666</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-04-14 22:37:18', '2017-07-17 20:04:59', 'a8f3ab3e-ef07-4661-b92d-c90cc3034378'),
 ('20', '237', 'en_us', 'Advertising Packages', '[{\"col3\":\"Weekly\",\"col1\":\"$45\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"35 commercials, 21 live reads\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Monthly\",\"col1\":\"$110\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"140 commercials, 84 live reads\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Semester\",\"col1\":\"$350\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"560 commercials, 336 live reads\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-05-31 20:18:40', '2017-07-17 19:25:57', '795e3fd1-e1c5-44cd-bc45-bd1049e02101'),
 ('22', '366', 'en_us', 'Newscasts', '[{\"col3\":\"Weekly\",\"col1\":\"$100\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Monthly\",\"col1\":\"$175\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Semester\",\"col1\":\"$450\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '<p>Includes a 10-second live read and logo shown\nduring opening and closing, as well as two\n30-second spots during the local newscasts at\n6 p.m., Monday–Friday. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-07-06 19:39:06', '2017-07-17 19:31:02', 'b3109b89-4f3b-4557-9feb-8c52d2b2097e'),
 ('23', '367', 'en_us', 'Original Programming', '[{\"col3\":\"Weekly\",\"col1\":\"$50\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Monthly\",\"col1\":\"$75\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '<p>Includes a 10-second live read and logo shown\nduring opening and closing billboards and two\n30-second spots during the show. Contact your\naccount executive for a list of shows and times. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-07-06 19:39:06', '2017-07-17 19:31:02', '9849e5a3-9587-4dbc-921e-0e3fb68c1726'),
 ('24', '376', 'en_us', 'Mobile DJ Service', '[{\"col3\":\"\",\"col1\":\"$50\\/hour + $50 set-up\\/tear down fee\",\"col5\":\"$15 travel fee (if event is outside of Portage County)\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '<p>BSR provides mobile DJ services for event both on and off campus, including: student organization events formals, proms, dances, sporting events, birthday parties, corporate events. and weddings..</p><p>For more information, please contact Tami Bongiorni at tbongior@kent.edu or 330-672-6306</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"col1\":\"Price\",\"col2\":\"Alternative Price\"}]', '2017-07-17 19:25:57', '2017-07-17 19:25:57', 'defec226-6539-4ffb-92a4-5df76c9b07c5'),
 ('25', '377', 'en_us', 'Digital Advertising', '[{\"col3\":\"Weekly\",\"col1\":\"$35\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '<p>Blacksquirrelradio.com is the first place listeners\nvisit to live-stream music, read the latest music\nreviews and find upcoming shows in the area.\nThe 728x90 banner ad links directly to your site\nand ad design services are included. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"col1\":\"Price\",\"col2\":\"Alternative Price\"}]', '2017-07-17 19:25:57', '2017-07-17 19:25:57', '5b188987-0820-40b0-9f9e-14843e940772'),
 ('26', '378', 'en_us', 'Radio Show Sponsorships', '[{\"col3\":\"Weekly\",\"col1\":\"$45\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Monthly\",\"col1\":\"$150\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '<p>Includes a 10-second live read for the show\nopening and closing. Shows run one time per\nweek and are two hours long. Contact your\naccount executive for complete show listings. <br /></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"col1\":\"Price\",\"col2\":\"Alternative Price\"}]', '2017-07-17 19:25:57', '2017-07-17 19:25:57', '55fb1ef8-911f-474f-8ac2-b11d01bddcd5'),
 ('27', '379', 'en_us', 'KSU Football Sponsorships', '[{\"col3\":\"Per game\",\"col1\":\"$175\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '<p>BSR commentates live at Kent State home\nfootball games and hosts pre-game, halftime\nand post-game shows.\n</p>\n<p>The official sponsorship includes live reads\nthroughout the shows and your business’ logo\nfeatured in The Kent Stater promotional ads. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"col1\":\"Price\",\"col2\":\"Alternative Price\"}]', '2017-07-17 19:25:57', '2017-07-17 19:25:57', '69717331-4549-4438-86d7-5fca1cf88025'),
 ('28', '380', 'en_us', 'Election Coverage', '[{\"col3\":\"Election Sponsor\",\"col1\":\"$450\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '<p>TV2 provides the campus and Portage County\nresidents local and national results in the live\nNovember election show. The show concludes\nwhen results are final and is no less than two\nhours in length.<br /></p>\n<p>The Election Sponsorship includes a minimum\nof two 30-second commercials, and\npromotional ads in both The Kent Stater and\nRecord-Courier. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"col1\":\"Price\",\"col2\":\"Alternative Price\"}]', '2017-07-17 19:29:30', '2017-07-17 19:31:02', '5611d9ee-7dfc-49c6-98ae-27b11ec58e1b'),
 ('29', '381', 'en_us', 'Non-Commercial Sponsorship', '[{\"col3\":\"Weekly\",\"col1\":\"$25\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '<p>Clients without commercials are eligible to\nappear on TV2. Non-commercial sponsorships\ninclude two name mentions, two 10-second\nlive reads and either a logo or slide of\ninformation shown. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"col1\":\"Price\",\"col2\":\"Alternative Price\"}]', '2017-07-17 19:29:30', '2017-07-17 19:31:02', 'adc992c3-7811-4f15-918d-e68679d783f9'),
 ('30', '382', 'en_us', 'Kent Roosevelt Vs. Ravenna High School Football', '[{\"col3\":\"Broadcast Sponsor\",\"col1\":\"$600\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '<p>The September 9th football game will be\nbroadcasted in its entirety on TV2 and\nreplays of the full broadcast will occur\nthroughout the weekend.</p>\n<p>TV2’s extensive sponsorship includes:</p><ul><li>Four 30-second commercials</li><li>Promotional mention using the sponsor’s<br />tagline and logo </li><li>Two 10-second live reads </li><li>Promotional mention in The Kent Stater<br />and Record-Courier ads </li><li>Complimentary replays of the game </li><li>One commercial in each Monday night<br />Sports Corner (10 total) </li><li>One commercial in each Friday Night<br />Frenzy (10 total) </li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"col1\":\"Price\",\"col2\":\"Alternative Price\"}]', '2017-07-17 19:29:30', '2017-07-17 19:31:02', '396e84f1-f338-4d85-b3b2-63ff1149df30'),
 ('31', '383', 'en_us', 'Display Ads', '[{\"col3\":\"Half Page\",\"col1\":\"$215\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Full Page\",\"col1\":\"$425\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Inside Cover\",\"col1\":\"$500\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Back Cover\",\"col1\":\"$600\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '<p><strong>WEB BONUS:</strong>\n</p>\n<p>All magazine ads also\ninclude a banner ad on\nthe magazine’s website\nfor one month.\n</p>\n<p>Additional months can\nbe purchased for only\n$25 per month. </p>\n<p><strong>MULTI-MAGAZINE\nDISCOUNT</strong>\n</p>\n<p>Run in three or more\nstudent-produced\nmagazines and get\n10% off all ads.\n</p>\n<p>Run in all six magazines\nand get 20% off all ads. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"col1\":\"Price\",\"col2\":\"Alternative Price\"}]', '2017-07-17 19:34:54', '2017-07-17 19:35:13', '474ac175-c02c-4127-888d-8a1f1f5987a7'),
 ('32', '384', 'en_us', 'Classifieds', '[{\"col3\":\"Cost Per Word\",\"col1\":\"35\\u00a2\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Extras\",\"col1\":\"$1\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Logo\\/picture\",\"col1\":\"$3 (black & white only)\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"col1\":\"Price\",\"col2\":\"Alternative Price\"}]', '2017-07-17 19:38:39', '2017-07-17 20:04:59', '5587f9c7-6291-4d30-b6a9-59e1cc0f8e88'),
 ('33', '385', 'en_us', 'Online Classifieds', '[{\"col3\":\"Daily\",\"col1\":\"$4\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Friday\",\"col1\":\"$5\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"(includes Saturday & Sunday)\"},{\"col3\":\"Monthly\",\"col1\":\"$75\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '<p>Classified ads on Kentwired.com are text-only ads\nbut may include an automatic link to your website,\nas well as direct call capabilities to a listed phone\nnumber from a viewer’s mobile device. All classified\nadvertisements are pre-pay only. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"col1\":\"Price\",\"col2\":\"Alternative Price\"}]', '2017-07-17 19:57:10', '2017-07-17 19:57:10', '6793448a-c847-498b-8d20-922afbedb8b0'),
 ('34', '386', 'en_us', '', '[{\"col3\":\"\",\"col1\":\"\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"\"}]', '<p>Kent State University Independent Films (KSUIF)\nhas produced four full-length films, a Telly award-\nwinning music video, and client-based short videos.</p>\n<p>The group is focused on the growth of digital media\nproduction at KSU and brings a new, vibrant partner\nto Kent State Student Media. <i>Hell at Heathridge</i>, a\nsupernatural thriller that premiered in 2013, can be found in 800 Family Video stores across the U.S.\nand Canada. <i>Unlucky</i>, a romantic comedy, will be\navailable in Family Video this fall.</p>\n<p>Sponsorships, product placement, poster\nsponsorship and producer credit opportunities\nare available for the next film. For more\ninformation, please contact Tami Bongiorni at\ntbongior@kent.edu or 330-672-6306. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"col1\":\"Price\",\"col2\":\"Alternative Price\"}]', '2017-07-17 20:02:51', '2017-07-17 20:02:51', '7e9e9b8f-6058-4ab6-b3e6-38c56e0a1201'),
 ('35', '388', 'en_us', 'The Kent Stater', '[{\"col3\":\"300-word story with multiple photos\\/images\",\"col1\":\"$795\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"Equivalent to a half page, full color ad\"}]', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"col1\":\"Price\",\"col2\":\"Alternative Price\"}]', '2017-07-18 18:46:00', '2017-07-25 19:21:19', 'c32ceec5-aa0f-4d60-b19c-26a77a7df45c'),
 ('36', '389', 'en_us', 'Kentwired.com or Kentcribs.com', '[{\"col3\":\"300-word story with multiple photos\\/images \",\"col1\":\"$695\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"Appears as featured story on the homepage and links to its own page. Also includes link to your website\"}]', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"col1\":\"Price\",\"col2\":\"Alternative Price\"}]', '2017-07-18 18:46:00', '2017-07-25 19:21:19', '0664373c-850e-4fee-834d-f3111d54e5fa'),
 ('37', '390', 'en_us', 'Transitions Magazine', '[{\"col3\":\"250-word story with multiple photos\\/images\",\"col1\":\"$545\",\"col5\":\"\",\"col2\":\"\",\"col4\":\"Equivalent to a full-page, full-color ad\"}]', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"col1\":\"Price\",\"col2\":\"Alternative Price\"}]', '2017-07-18 18:46:00', '2017-07-25 19:21:19', '80ff65ec-2d51-488c-97dd-de7e3d43308b');
INSERT INTO `craft_matrixcontent_faq` (`id`, `elementId`, `locale`, `field_faqs_question`, `field_faqs_answer`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES
 ('1', '231', 'en_us', 'How can I become a student media leader?', '<p>Leaders of each Student Media partner are selected by the Student Media Board in the fall and spring of each year for the following semester or semesters. To be considered, you must be must have at least a verified cumulative 2.25 Grade Point Average at the time of application and maintain a cumulative 2.25 GPA and be in good standing with the University during your term as leader.  To be a compensated student leader, you must be enrolled in a minimum of eight credit hours as an undergraduate student and a minimum of six as a graduate student during their term. You do not need to be majors enrolled in the School of Journalism and Mass Communication.  Candidates applying for leadership positions in the JMC-co-curricular units must have related experience to be considered an applicant.</p>', '2017-05-11 03:35:13', '2017-07-17 20:44:47', '0629520b-f544-4c06-b6b8-4fe0461e7ee4'),
 ('2', '261', 'en_us', 'Can I get paid while working for Student Media?', '<p>Yes. Student Media offers hundreds of paid positions each semester across our 10 Student Media partners. Contact us for more information. </p>', '2017-06-01 20:33:12', '2017-07-17 20:44:47', '7cd2d58d-8599-4cf2-a889-8fc2cc3963a1'),
 ('3', '262', 'en_us', 'Can I study abroad and still be involved in Student Media?', '<p>Yes. Student Media supports students who opt for a semester abroad. Sometimes this can fit into a media outlet\'s content plan for that semester. Also, studying abroad will not affect your ability to continue on a path to a leadership position, if you so choose. </p>', '2017-06-01 20:33:12', '2017-07-17 20:44:47', '6be4c2fb-1710-4d2a-b3ad-d09ad3a2593c'),
 ('4', '263', 'en_us', 'Who makes the hiring decisions for Student Media?', '<p>It depends on the position you are seeking:</p>\n<ul><li>Top leaders for each media partner are selected by the Student Media Board</li><li>Staff members within each media partner are selected by the student leader in consultation with the adviser</li><li>Staff members in the Student Media office are selected by the professional staff. </li></ul>', '2017-06-01 20:33:12', '2017-07-17 20:44:47', 'b39b7930-7f51-4dcc-96e1-169bf0d5f7e3'),
 ('5', '264', 'en_us', 'How many hours can I work?', '<p>That depends on your position and the needs of your outlet. You should talk with your student leader and adviser about the specific needs of each position. If you are in a paid position, you cannot work more than 28 hours each week.  </p>', '2017-06-01 20:33:12', '2017-07-17 20:44:47', '96d6e875-290e-4336-b07d-af726bb4c35b'),
 ('6', '265', 'en_us', 'If I don\'t see a position I like, can I still work in Student Media?', '<p>Probably, let\'s talk.  Student Media is growing and changing as rapidly as the professional fields we strive to emulate. So, if a position doesn\'t exist (and it\'s generally within the wheelhouse of media and communications), let\'s talk and figure out how to make it happen. </p>', '2017-06-01 20:33:12', '2017-07-17 20:44:47', '263f70f7-2928-47a2-b8a6-8860a11d971d'),
 ('7', '282', 'en_us', 'Can I earn academic credit for my work in Student Media?', '<p>Consult with your academic adviser to see if this is allowed through your program. Some schools allow this and others don\'t.  Student Media cooperates with the various academic units on campus. </p>', '2017-06-06 15:54:11', '2017-07-17 20:44:47', '5ac55dc7-b92a-400a-8c78-0d61a5923007'),
 ('8', '283', 'en_us', 'How long does my employment last once I\'m hired in Student Media?', '<p>Employment length varies from individual to individual and is decided by the the media partner student leader.  Most last until the end of the semester, but other arrangements are possible.  Please talk with the student leader for the media partner with which you work or for which you are interested in working. Student leaders have the responsibility to remove staff members who are not performing well and/or are not following rules and regulations of Student Media.  </p>', '2017-06-06 15:54:11', '2017-07-17 20:44:47', '46e61ec1-5c97-417f-8327-d277b2b9b05c'),
 ('9', '284', 'en_us', 'Do I have to reapply for a job in Student Media every semester?', '<p>This depends on your job and the media parter for which you work.  If your work for a media partner where a new editor is elected each semester, you\'ll likely have to reapply.  Some partners have student leaders elected for an entire academic year. It\'s possible that this leader will hire positions for the whole year. This is their decision. </p>', '2017-06-06 15:54:11', '2017-07-17 20:44:47', '36bb0e55-66b2-4506-bc42-f371f0b8863b'),
 ('10', '285', 'en_us', 'Can I work for more than one outlet at the same time during a semester?', '<p>Yes. The university limits your paid hours to 28 hours per week in total for all university jobs for which you are paid.  </p>', '2017-06-06 15:54:11', '2017-07-17 20:44:47', '1b700be5-fb52-4cea-af60-2b24f4c7b167'),
 ('11', '286', 'en_us', 'Can I volunteer at a Student Media publication?', '<p>Yes. Some jobs are paid, others are volunteer or on a contributor basis. Check with the student leader for each organization to see what opportunities exist at the moment for that media partner. </p>', '2017-06-06 15:54:11', '2017-07-17 20:44:47', '9ce72e1d-c6c5-4f3f-a338-01fece1384a1'),
 ('12', '287', 'en_us', 'Who has editorial control over content?', '<p>Student editors and student managers have sole authority to determine content for the media they lead and in turn take full responsibility for the content decisions made.</p>', '2017-06-06 15:54:11', '2017-07-17 20:44:47', '7fb8dd0d-649b-498e-b03f-5dd7a690f173'),
 ('13', '288', 'en_us', 'Where can I listen to Black Squirrel Radio?', '<p><a href=\"http://blacksquirrelradio.com\">http://blacksquirrelradio.com</a></p>', '2017-06-06 15:54:11', '2017-07-17 20:44:47', 'd9313a1a-64f0-450a-b21a-eae9bde5fda6'),
 ('14', '289', 'en_us', 'On which channel is TV2 broadcast?', '<p>We broadcast on channel 2.2 on Kent State\'s campus, and off-campus on Charter Spectrum channel 16.  TV2 also streams live and archives shows at www.kentwired.com/tv2.</p>', '2017-06-06 15:54:11', '2017-07-17 20:44:47', '5ae27fc4-1af6-43bd-a767-f01f4e7339b1');
